# Blog posts

- Add Markdown (or MDX) files under `src/content/blog/`.
- Filename becomes the URL slug: `my-topic.md` → `/blog/my-topic`.
- Required frontmatter (see `src/content.config.ts`):

```yaml
---
title: 'Post title'
description: 'One-line summary for SEO and listings'
pubDate: 'May 11 2026'
heroImage: '../../assets/blog-placeholder-1.jpg'  # optional
updatedDate: 'May 12 2026'  # optional
---
```

- Run `npm run dev` and check `/blog`, the post URL, and `/rss.xml`.
- Keep voice consistent with existing posts: practical, first-person, learning-in-public.
